Package: linux-image-4.19.325-samsung-a13
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux kernel for Samsung Galaxy A13
 This package contains the Linux kernel for the Samsung Galaxy A13 device.
 .
 Note: This package only ships the kernel image and modules, you should probably
 look at the linux-bootimage-4.19.325-samsung-a13 package for a bootimage suitable
 for Android boot loaders.

Package: linux-bootimage-4.19.325-samsung-a13
Architecture: arm64
