Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         linux-image-4.19.325-samsung-a13 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Linux kernel for Samsung Galaxy A13 - Android Boot Image
 This package contains the Linux kernel for the Samsung Galaxy A13 device.
 .
 Note: This package ships an Android Boot Image bundled with Halium's
 initramfs.

